Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lymph nodes' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Multiple pathologically enlarged lymph nodes' radio button is enabled
And 'Localization acc. to IASCL' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Multiple pathologically enlarged lymph nodes' radio button
Then 'Diameter of largest LN, SAD*' input field is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Localization acc. to IASCL' radio button
Then '1: Supraclavicular zone' radio button is enabled
And '2-4: Superior mediastinal nodes' radio button is enabled
And '5-6: Aortic LN' radio button is enabled
And '7-9: Inferior mediastinal LN' radio button is enabled
And '10-14: Hilar, (inter)lobar and (sub)segmental LN' radio button is enabled

And 'Diameter, SAD*' input field is enabled
And 'Reference lesion acc. to RECIST' checkbox is enabled
And 'Confluent' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled

When I select '1: Supraclavicular zone' radio button
Then '1R: Supraclavicular, low cervical and sternal notch nodes right' radio button is enabled
And '1L: Supraclavicular, low cervical and sternal notch nodes left' radio button is enabled

When I select '2-4: Superior mediastinal nodes' radio button
Then '2R: Upper paratracheal LN right' radio button is enabled
And '2L: Upper paratracheal LN left' radio button is enabled
And '3A: Prevascular LN' radio button is enabled
And '3P: Retrotracheal LN' radio button is enabled
And '4R: Lower paratracheal lymph nodes right' radio button is enabled
And '4L: Lower paratracheal lymph nodes left' radio button is enabled

When I select '5-6: Aortic LN' radio button
Then '5: Subaortic LN/aortopulmonary window' radio button is enabled
And '6: Para-aortic LN' radio button is enabled

When I select '7-9: Inferior mediastinal LN' radio button
Then '7: Infracarinal LN' radio button is enabled
And '8: Paraesophageal LN' radio button is enabled
And '9R: Pulmonary lig. nodes right' radio button is enabled
And '9L: Pulmonary lig. nodes left' radio button is enabled

When I select '10-14: Hilar, (inter)lobar and (sub)segmental LN' radio button
Then '10: Hilar lymph nodes' radio button is enabled
And '11: Interlobar LN' radio button is enabled
And '12: Lobar LN' radio button is enabled
And '13: Segmental LN' radio button is enabled
And '14: Subsegmental LN' radio button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

When I enter any value between 1 and 99 in 'Diameter, SAD*' input field
Then 'Suspicious' checkbox is enabled
And 'Preserved fatty hilum' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Calcification' checkbox
Then 'Complete' radio button is enabled
And 'Eggshell pattern' radio button is enabled 
